sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant IR_Sensor
    participant FPGA_Top
    participant PC_UART
    
    User->>IR_Sensor: Drückt Taste (z.B. Power)
    IR_Sensor->>FPGA_Top: Sendet NEC Frame (67.5ms)
    Note over FPGA_Top: EdgeDetector synchronisiert Signal
    Note over FPGA_Top: PulseTimer misst Pulsbreiten
    Note over FPGA_Top: NECDecoder validiert Frame
    FPGA_Top->>FPGA_Top: set data_valid = 1
    Note over FPGA_Top: Formatter wandelt Byte in ASCII
    FPGA_Top->>PC_UART: UART TX: "A"
    FPGA_Top->>PC_UART: UART TX: ":"
    FPGA_Top->>PC_UART: UART TX: "0"
    FPGA_Top->>PC_UART: UART TX: "0"
    FPGA_Top->>PC_UART: ...
    FPGA_Top->>PC_UART: UART TX: "\n"
    Note right of PC_UART: Terminal zeigt: "A:00 C:45"
